{"article_id":"CUQ3u2u5gdF2wae3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Vice President Joe Biden has yet to rule out a 2016 presidential campaign","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"and is likely to wait beyond August","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"to decide ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"several Democrats say ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"allowing him to watch","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"as the contest unfolds","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"before determining","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"whether he could make a viable late entry into the race .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"While Biden has done little","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"to lay the groundwork for a possible challenge to Hillary Clinton and the rest of the Democratic field ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"CNN has learned","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"that a group of his friends and advisers are still urging him to keep the door open .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"He has not discounted those arguments ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Democrats close to him say ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and he feels no pressure","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"to reach a decision by the end of summer","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"as he once suggested .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"`` I know","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"there are a lot of people around the country","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"who would like to see him run","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and think","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"he 'd be a terrific president , ''","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"said Sen. Tom Carper , a Delaware Democrat and longtime friend of the Biden family .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"`` They are biding their time","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"and holding their fire","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"until Joe is ready to make that decision . ''","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"With the Iowa caucuses and New Hampshire primary six months away , Biden is the leading figure","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Democrats believe","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"they could turn to","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"if they needed to find an alternative to Clinton ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"whose favorability ratings have taken a deep hit","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"as her email use while secretary of state is still drawing controversy .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"The prospects","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"of Biden running ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"his advocates say ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"are rooted not only in his own ambitions ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"but also with an eye toward helping the party put forward a stronger nominee","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"to run against Republicans .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Yet it remains an open question whether voters would be open to effectively a third term of President Barack Obama ,","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"since Biden is tightly linked to every achievement and shortfall of the administration .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"Liberals have rallied behind Sen. Bernie Sanders , the Democratic socialist from Vermont ,","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"but his general election prospects are far from certain .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Biden , 72 , has a large and loyal collection of friends and advisers from more than four decades in Washington .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"Yet even inside his sprawling constellation ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"affectionately known as `` Biden World , ''","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"deep divisions exist over the wisdom","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"of him making another bid for the presidency .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Conversations this week with people close to Biden , from his home base in Delaware to Washington and beyond , suggest agreement on three points :","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"He has not made up his mind .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Anyone","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"who believes","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"he has","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"is wrong .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"And he should be allowed to decide on his own timeframe .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"`` It is very late in the presidential cycle","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"to build the infrastructure ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"but the vice president enjoys a unique level of experience and respect , ''","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"said Sen. Chris Coons , a Delaware Democrat ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"who is staying neutral","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"until Biden decides .","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"`` He has the ability","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"to wait later in this process than almost any other Democrat . ''","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"Two months after his oldest son , Beau , died of brain cancer ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"the vice president has slowly returned to his duties at the White House and his residence at the Naval Observatory ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"where he invited lawmakers over Thursday","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"to discuss the Iran nuclear deal .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Friends say","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"he is still grieving ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"which is also why he feels no urgency","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"to make a decision","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and has not intensely focused on the presidential race .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"But Biden 's future is suddenly being examined in a new context ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"several Democrats partial to Biden","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"say ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"in the wake of lingering questions","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"about whether Clinton or her aides mishandled classified information on the private email server","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"she used as secretary of state .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"Even as his admirers implore him to consider running ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"many other Democrats believe","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"the realistic window is closing , particularly fundraisers and key activists","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"who play a critical role","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"in selecting the party 's nominee .","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"Clinton has moved swiftly to lock up support from many of those so-called superdelegates ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"which would complicate efforts","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"to slow her momentum as the party 's frontrunner .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Roxanna Moritz , the Democratic auditor of Scott County in Iowa , had been holding out hope","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"that she would hear from Biden .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"She was inspired by a grassroots Draft Biden movement","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"and believed","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"he would be the strongest nominee for the Democratic Party .","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"But the only calls","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"she received","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"were from the campaigns of Clinton and Bernie Sanders ,","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"so she made a decision two weeks ago .","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"`` I signed on with Hillary , ''","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Moritz said Friday .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"`` It was hard to make that choice for me","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"because I 'm very attached to Biden .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"Personally , I like the man .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"I like the values","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"he 's brought to the country .","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"But it seems like he 's being steamrolled .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"I think","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"it would be hard for him to catch up . ''","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Yet the silence from Biden has n't sapped the hope from all of his supporters ,","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"even though they recognize","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"his focus is elsewhere .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"he 's ready yet , ''","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"said Mary Carey Foley , a top Biden supporter in New Hampshire ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"who last spoke to the vice president at Beau Biden 's funeral in early June .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"`` He 's devastated .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"His head is in it ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"but his heart has to catch up , ''","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"`` And Joe Biden has a big heart . ''","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"Supporters like Foley say","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Biden appeared inclined to mount a bid","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"before his son fell ill ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"and had begun mapping out a fundraising plan","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"to compete with the massive hauls","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"many expect Clinton to pull in .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"His family","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"-- including Beau , before his death --","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"have encouraged a run ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"though any talk of politics was put on hold during the mourning period .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"On Saturday , New York Times columnist Maureen Dowd reported","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"as Beau Biden was dying ,","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"he tried to make his father promise to run in 2016 in an effort","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"to not let the presidency be turned back over to the Clintons .","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"`` Dad , it 's who you are , ''","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"Hunter said ,","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"joining his brother ,","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"Dowd reported .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"The vice president 's office has declined interview requests","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"and has issued the same statement for weeks about Biden 's intentions .","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"`` The Biden family is going through a difficult time right now , ''","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"Kendra Barkoff , a Biden spokeswoman , said Friday .","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"`` Any speculation about the views of the vice president or his family about his political future is premature and inappropriate . ''","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"Still , the latest CNN national poll finds","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"15 % of Democratic and Democratic-leaning registered voters are behind Biden , just a bit behind Sanders ' 19 % .","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"He also tops the second-choice list","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"with 37 % of Democratic registered voters choosing him .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"Among those","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"who say","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"Clinton is their first choice ,","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"he 's the clear leader as a second choice ,","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"with 50 % of Clinton backers saying","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"Biden 's their next pick .","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"The group Draft Biden ,","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"established","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"to encourage a run by the vice president ,","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"say","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"supporters have held more than 400 events in 21 different states in recent months .","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"Momentum for a Biden run has n't slowed ,","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"organizers say ,","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"as Clinton begins laying out policy positions in early voting states .","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"`` Democratic supporters are hungry for a race .","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"They want a lively debate , ''","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"said Will Pierce , Draft Biden 's executive director .","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"he feared `` Democratic falloff ''","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"if Clinton does n't face a challenger","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"that voters believe","depth":15},{"id":166,"text":"could be elected president .","depth":15},{"id":167,"text":"Jon Cooper , a former Obama fundraiser","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"who serves as Draft Biden 's National Finance Chair ,","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"his conversations with Democratic donors has left him convinced","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"the vice president could raise the cash","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"needed to compete against Clinton .","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"The bond between Biden and Obama has grown closer in the second term","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"and Biden is seen again and again at the president 's side .","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"`` Partly because of the very deep reservoir of support","depth":15},{"id":176,"text":"we 'll find among Obama supporters , bundlers and donors ,","depth":15},{"id":177,"text":"I think","depth":15},{"id":178,"text":"the Biden campaign will be able to tap into that overnight , ''","depth":15},{"id":179,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"`` He will be able literally within 24 hours put a strong fundraising structure in place . ''","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":361,"left":0,"right":360,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":360,"left":206,"right":359,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":188,"right":205,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":184,"right":187,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":1,"right":183,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":183,"left":182,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":185,"right":186,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":205,"left":191,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":189,"right